desc        short help text.  index of commands
long_desc   longer help.  'app help subcommand' shows subcommand's help

option      option to pass to options hash
  required  t/f
  default   anything
  type      string/hash/array/numeric/boolean
  aliases   short options
  banner    help text
class_option option for entire class

subcommand  useful for making a suite of commands, ie git.
